Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.34,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}固く固く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:23.57,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}ひと結び　人を結んで
